english:
  title: 'Night Sitting: Immediate Impressions'
  author: Heo Jong
  language: eng
  text: |-
    The courtyard overflows with flowers and moonlight,
    Cast upon the silken window screen—
    Flowers drift too easily with the wind,
    The moon shifts too easily from its place.

    Bright moon, you will surely shine tomorrow night,
    But all my sorrow, all my worry,
    Clings to these fading flowers.
